$TDOC | 90% of the $3.5 Trillion spent annually on health care is spent on chronic pain and mental health issues per the CDC.  CloudMD’s integrated telehealth technology will be used in clinical practice to provide patient centric, continuity of care.

CloudMD (a.k.a. the ‘Canadian TelaDoc’) continues to embark on its U.S. expansion. The acquisition of Benchmark strengthens CloudMD’s digital footprint across North America. The acquisition also brings cross selling synergies across Benchmark’s 200 clinics and its geographical footprint in 35 states. Benchmark’s suite of software solutions provides CloudMD (ticker: $DOCRF) with significant distribution channels into the U.S.

